collectionMetadata.name: Enrolment - Secondary, By Age
collectionMetadata.description:
1) Normal(T) figures include students in Specialised Schools. These students are taking the ITE Skills Certificate (ISC) course or in a 2-year work-study programme after completing ISC.
2)	All Secondary 5 students are in the Normal (Academic) course.
3)	Includes Government, Govt-Aided, Independent, Specialised Independent and Specialised schools.
4)	Age is as at the start of the year.
